Fwd ISDA Master agreement CSAHi Marie Sorry to be a pain about this but our business people are very keen to finalize this agreement and I wondered if you have any comments for me Thanks Katryna Original Message Subject ISDA Master agreement CSA Date Thu Oct From Katryna Murtagh ReplyTo Organization Morgan Stanley To Marie NRONcom Dear Marie I note from your email of August that you were going to get back to us with your further comments once Sara Shackelton returned from vacation in September I wonder if you have now had a chance to discuss this issue with Sara and if you have any feed back for me Thanks very much for your ongoing assistance in this matter Kind regards Katryna
